          "value": "ContentHistoryType/Modification (inline)",
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "A record of a modification made to a CAPEC entry, identifying the modifier,\ntheir organization, the date of modification, the importance of the change,\nand any related comments. Modifications that change the meaning of the entry\nshould be marked as Critical importance.",
